* Z0 = 50 Ohms, Keff = 6.972
microstrip_calc 0.877e-3 1e-3 1.0 3e-5 1.72e-8 0.0 9.60 0.0 1e10
* Z0 = 75 Ohms, Keff = 2.033
microstrip_calc 1.379e-3 1e-3 1.0 3e-5 1.72e-8 0.0 2.55 0.0 1e6
*
  </STDEX>
</EXAMPLE>

